INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (581, '2012-06-05 11:23:00', 4, 146, '<p>BBC created Planet Earth series a few years a;.</p>\n\n<p>The trailer can be seen here: <a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/nature/collections/p00fxg1n\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/nature/collections/p00fxg1n</a> - if you ; to 0.25 (screenshot below) it shows a sky diver jumping into a forest hole - I wanted to know where that is filmed.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://i.stack.imgur.com/6YpzB.jpg\" alt=\"screen-bbc-planet-earth-sky-diver\"></p>', 1132, 196, '2012-06-07 19:24:03', '2012-06-07 19:24:03', 'In the BBC Planet Earth trailer - where is the sky diver jumping?', '<documentary>', '2012-06-09 11:23:00');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (582, '2012-06-05 13:02:21', 5, 395, '<p>The Paths of the Dead is where Ara;rn, Le;las and Gimli ; to recruit the undead army to fight for ;ndor. </p>\n\n<p>The most detailed map of Middle Earth I could find is <a href=\"http://blog.lefigaro.fr/hightech/assets_c/2011/06/middle-earth-map-33096.html\">here</a>.</p>\n\n<p>From reading on <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paths_of_the_Dead\">Wikipedia</a> it mentions all the places it\'s near like Harrowdale and Dimholt but I can\'t find any of these on the map so I can\'t figure out where the Paths of the Dead is.</p>', 1612, 889, NULL, '2012-06-05 14:04:43', 'Where in Middle Earth is the Paths of the Dead?', '<plot-explanation><lord-of-the-rings>', '2012-06-22 13:02:21');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (583, '2012-06-06 09:28:29', 5, 470, '<p>Usually Big Blockbusters are timed to be released in major countries at roughly the same time. This even includes movies that are dubbed for localised version. </p>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1446714/releaseinfo\" rel=\"nofollow\">London premiere was on 31 May 2012</a> but the German release will be on 9 August 2012.</p>\n\n<p>Is there any information why the German version ;t a 2 month delay?</p>', 276, 1020, '2012-06-11 14:33:01', '2012-07-23 09:35:09', 'Why is the German version of Prometheus released 2 months after the world premiere?', '<prometheus><film-industry>', '2012-07-13 09:28:29');
