INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (635, '2012-06-21 10:55:40', 13, 586, '<p>The two franchises are held by two separate companies. One, Sony, holds the rights to Spider-man 4-7, and are obliged to continue this line or give up the rights to the movies. The other, Marvel Studios, owns the rights to the Avengers and the subsidiary characters.</p>\n\n<p>Under what circumstances might Spider-man join the Avengers? Are movie rights buys outs uncommon? Could a serenity/firefly-esque loophole be pulled off? Could the two studios \'team up\'?</p>', 1142, 406, '2012-06-21 18:34:07', '2012-06-22 15:55:47', 'What would have to happen to merge the Spider-man franchise and the Avengers franchise?', '<avengers><spider-man>', '2012-08-03 10:55:40');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (636, '2012-06-21 22:13:13', 4, 148, '<p>In the 1989 movie <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0097737/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Leviathan</a> the crew finds an old Russian submarine and brings aboard a bottle of Vodka. After drinking the Vodka members of the crew mutate into a sea creature that attacks the rest of the crew.</p>\n\n<p>Isn\'t their DNA matured by a virus in the bottle? Wouldn\'t the alcohol in the Vodka act as a disinfectant and kill any viruses, and how did the virus get into the bottle in the first place?</p>', 1590, 1522, '2014-02-18 16:59:42', '2014-02-18 16:59:42', 'Why does the crew get infected from the Vodka in Leviathan', '<leviathan>', '2012-08-02 22:13:13');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (637, '2012-06-21 22:28:54', 2, 6859, '<p>I watched a <strong>horror</strong> movie about 4~5 years a; that it was a story about newly married couple who would spend their honeymoon in a remote house/cabin. Then strange things start to happen. They hear the bell and it was a strange child seems to be lost. They dismiss the child, but it come back again. So the man left the house for some reason and the children start to scare the woman. At the end the haunting becomes more frequent and the children enters the house. The couple tries to run away but the car doesn\'t works. </p>\n\n<p>I don\'t remember much more.</p>\n\n<p>Anyone knows the name of this movie??</p>', 480, 715, '2012-06-22 15:14:55', '2014-02-17 03:55:23', 'Movie about a haunted couple at their honeymoon in a cabin', '<identify-this-movie><horror>', '2012-07-17 22:28:54');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (638, '2012-06-22 01:57:54', 9, 337, '<p>The the last time we see the heroin in No Country for Old Men, Lewellyn Moss is present. He finds they money and heroin, but takes only takes the money. </p>\n\n<p>The next time we are at the scene, Anton Chigur kills the two men and pursues the money. The heroin is not shown or discussed. Did Chigur get the heroin?  </p>\n\n<p>The next time we are at the scene, the heroin is ;ne, and Ed Tom Bell knows the heroin was there, but is now ;ne.</p>\n\n<p>Did Moss or Chigur take the heroin? Was it someone else who came and took it?</p>', 1545, 1073, '2012-06-22 15:11:09', '2012-07-18 16:45:48', 'Who stole the heroin in No Country For Old Men?', '<plot-explanation><coen-brothers><no-country-for-old-men>', '2012-08-10 01:57:54');
