INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (796, '2012-08-13 09:45:53', 11, 1832, '<p>In the movie <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prometheus_%28film%29\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prometheus</a> the alien is born from the last \'human-alien\' of the planet they traveled to.</p>\n\n<p>But, how should it be interpreted? The alien is a mutation from the parasite inside the body of the other one? Or the alien is the real aspect of the others that is hiding inside some kind of armor?</p>', 538, 404, '2013-11-14 12:15:06', '2013-11-14 12:15:06', 'What\'s the real meaning of the birth of the alien in Prometheus?', '<plot-explanation><prometheus>', '2012-09-17 09:45:53');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (797, '2012-08-13 10:03:53', 5, 2002, '<p>In the final sequences of Alien, Ripley activates the self destruct sequence of the ship, Nostromo.</p>\n\n<p>After seeing the alien in front of the shuttle entrance, Ripley runs back to the control room and frantically tries to deactivate the self destruct.</p>\n\n<p>The whole sequence can be seen <a href=\"http://www.markta.co.uk/alien/chapter12.htm\">here in pictures</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Why would Ripley make this decision; what\'s the need for disabling the self-destruct?</p>\n\n<p>Basically she was dead anyway. Nowhere to ; and the alien was on to her. So it would just seem to be the best option to destruct the ship and the alien.</p>', 164, 1131, '2012-08-13 10:24:31', '2012-08-13 11:01:18', 'Why did Ripley try to deactivate the self-destruct sequence?', '<plot-explanation><alien>', '2012-09-23 10:03:53');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (798, '2012-08-13 16:58:44', 3, 279, '<p>In Vanishing on 7th Street, people disappear if they become engulfed in darkness.  At one point Paul is lying on the pool table and the kid went to the bathroom.  The lights flicker and Paul gets up.  He ends up finding his way into this tunnel.  When he reaches the end he looks back and all of the lights ; out.  The kid ;es back in and finds Paul missing.</p>\n\n<p>What is the meanign of the tunnel scene?  It seems that it didn\'t actually happen, but I\'m confused as to why it\'s included.</p>', 1080, 48, NULL, '2013-11-22 04:21:28', 'What was the meaning of the tunnel scene?', '<analysis><vanishing-on-7th-street>', '2012-10-10 16:58:44');
