INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (951, '2012-10-15 23:11:57', 4, 137400, '<p>I just watched the new movie with Emma Watson, <em>\"The Perks of Being a Wallflower\"</em>.</p>\n\n<p>The central theme of the movie is the relationship between Charlie and his aunt. He has been traumatized by her death, which he seems to feel responsible for, and has recurring flashbacks of her.</p>\n\n<p>I am not completely sure that I understood what was ;ing on with him and her. Did she sexually abuse him? If so, and he actually wished her death, why did he say to Sam that she (his aunt) was his favorite person ever?</p>\n\n<p>Also, what is the part about his best friend having killed himself? Who is he referring to?</p>', 56, 407, '2012-10-16 18:14:08', '2013-02-04 19:42:27', 'What did Charlie\'s aunt do?', '<plot-explanation><analysis><perks-of-being-wallflower><emma-watson>', '2012-12-10 23:11:57');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (952, '2012-10-15 23:50:50', 2, 684, '<p>Thriller about a group of kidnappers wearing Santa Claus masks and taking a group of kidnapees into a cave ? It could be from the early nineties or thereabouts. I remember very little from this movie. Is there an old man getting shot by a shotgun and falling over an aquarium? There may also have been a scene with the kidnapees swimming to safety through an underwater channel or something.</p>', 1312, 852, NULL, '2012-10-16 02:55:38', 'Thriller about a group of kidnappers wearing Santa Claus masks and taking a group of kidnapees into a cave?', '<identify-this-movie>', '2012-10-30 23:50:50');
