INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (1098, '2012-12-10 12:50:51', 2, 533, '<p>I vaguely remember watching a TV show some 20-odd years a;, but remember only a few details from the pilot episode:</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>This guy dies, and is told he has to ; back in time to watch over some teenager.</li>\n<li>In an attempt to make life easy for the teen and his family, he gives the teen a lottery ticket that he thinks will win millions of dollars. Instead, he missed a couple of numbers, and the teen won a much smaller amount.</li>\n<li>The guy is then invited to stay with the teen, and the guy looks up to heaven with a bit of a concerned look about how long he\'ll have to stay on earth before he can ; to heaven.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>If I remember correctly, the show also only lasted about 1 season. </p>', 1748, 1513, '2014-09-13 17:17:55', '2014-09-13 17:17:55', 'TV show from the late 80s, early 90s about guy who dies and ;es back in time to watch over family', '<identify-this-tv-show>', '2012-12-17 12:50:51');
