INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (1129, '2012-12-17 05:21:18', 1, 1221, '<p>In the S10E19 of <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0313043/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CSI:Miami</a>, Darren Vogel is also in the car which was driven by Sam (in the final segment of the episode). But after the accident, we see Sam is carried away by Horatio and Delko. Eddie Coster is shown dead. </p>\n\n<p>But only one dead body is taken away from the scene (which definitely has to be of Eddie\'s). So it makes a total of two people taken out from the scene.</p>\n\n<p>But there were three people in the car. What happened to Darren (the third person)?</p>', 783, 826, '2012-12-21 06:45:22', '2012-12-21 16:13:40', 'What happened to Darren Vogel in CSI:Miami?', '<plot-explanation><character><specific-scene><csi-miami>', '2013-02-08 05:21:18');
