INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (1433, '2013-02-24 10:05:31', 6, 427, '<p>My mother asked me to help her identify a movie she would like to rewatch. Her memory of it is sketchy at best though.</p>\n\n<p>The movie was released sometime in the 60s, it was in color and it was probably British production.</p>\n\n<p>She recalls a man ;ing through a forest following some feeling. The man encounters a fence with various warnings, passes that fence and finds something resembling a huge spider egg. That egg is emitting some waves that cause anxiety.</p>\n\n<p>Edit: additional details:</p>\n\n<p>Lengthy sentences of ;ing through the forest, the man is visibly lost, but drawn (by a feeling) in certain direction. It lasts for quite a while - nothing an action-packed series could afford, definitely a style of full movie. No catchy \"action\" music, mostly just rustling of leaves. Dry underbrush, fallen leaves - early spring or late fall. Later, upon finding the fence, he sneaks along the fence trying to spot whatever\'s inside for quite a while until he finds a spot with a view to the inside. The orb structure is a huge sphere - there are other buildings around it, and they are small by comparison. </p>\n\n<p>I\'m not quite sure if it\'s 60\'s - the clothes of the prota;nists are \"fashionable\" 60\'s clothing - slightly too short, slim trousers, a kind of hip suit.</p>', 1747, 276, '2013-03-08 21:43:29', '2014-02-02 05:18:16', 'A horror movie from the 60s, egg-like object', '<identify-this-movie>', '2013-03-20 10:05:31');
