INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (1490, '2013-03-13 21:41:16', 10, 293, '<p>In the movie \"Prometheus\" the android David flawlessly executes a seemingly endless range of tasks:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p>learns to read and speak an alien language</p></li>\n<li><p>shoots a basketball with precision</p></li>\n<li><p>keeps the spaceship tidy</p></li>\n<li><p>spelunks in a cave</p></li>\n<li><p>performs medical evaluations</p></li>\n<li><p>conducts scientific analysis</p></li>\n<li><p>pilots alien spacecraft</p></li>\n<li><p>makes witty remarks</p></li>\n<li><p>follows orders reliably, even with his head cut off</p></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>With all this in mind, <strong>why bring anyone but David (or perhaps multiple Davids) on the mission?</strong> Wouldn\'t it be obvious that humans, with all their flaws, would only reduce the odds of success?</p>', 1240, 353, '2013-03-13 22:41:54', '2013-03-14 15:21:16', 'In \"Prometheus\" why bring anyone but David-type androids?', '<plot-explanation><prometheus>', '2013-04-26 21:41:16');
