INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (1561, '2013-04-03 06:28:33', 3, 235, '<p>This may be set in china or somewhere in Asia.  </p>\n\n<p>A family had to flee their town because of an invasion or some emergency. They may be running from people searching for them. </p>\n\n<p>They are ;ne for months, maybe even a year. I remember a horrible husband forcing two women, one his wife, to pull a cart up a mountain. </p>\n\n<p>A young woman is separated from her husband and travels with them. The husband or boyfriend of this young woman searched for her for months and assumed she died. </p>\n\n<p>They find other families in the mountains, winter comes and people are starving and freezing. The quiet weak son dies and the father beats his wife after he finds out.</p>\n\n<p>Someone becomes pregnant and is devastated. </p>\n\n<p>A woman commits suicide and stumbles down a cliff. </p>\n\n<p>They eventually make it back to their home and the young woman is reunited with her husband or boyfriend. She is dirty and filthy and embarrassed but he still loves her. The other man wants payment for her.</p>', 281, 173, '2013-04-03 12:11:58', '2013-04-03 12:11:58', 'Identify a movie about an Asian family forced into the mountains in the winter', '<identify-this-movie>', '2013-05-26 06:28:33');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (1562, '2013-04-03 15:25:03', 6, 151, '<p>In Season three episode 2, the episode titled \"Smith and Jones\", the doctor lets the plasmavore suck out his blood in order for it to be captured, and passes out from the blood loss.  Martha comes to his rescue and performs cpr, but in the middle of it she somehow realized that he had two hears, and starts pumping his chest in two locations.</p>\n\n<p>I was confused as to how she knew he had two hearts.  How did she know?</p>', 2, 1785, NULL, '2013-04-03 15:36:38', 'How did Martha Jones know he had two hearts?', '<doctor-who>', '2013-05-05 15:25:03');
