lso seen at other places around StackExchange such as <a href=\"http://space.stackexchange.com/\">Space Exploration</a>, <a href=\"http://scifi.stackexchange.com/\">Sci-Fi &amp; Fantasy</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://movies.stackexchange.com/\">Movies &amp; TV</a>.</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>FB friend requests please note, I will not be \'friending\' people on FB who appear under a different name on FB than, here.  I am <em>tired</em> of adding friends that make me think \'And ..who is <em>that?</em>\'.</li>\n</ol>', 65, 246, 20);
